/docker.html.title: Docker
/docker.html.content:
• enable bash completion

    curl https://rawgithubusercontentcom/docker/dockerce/master/components/cli/contrib/completion/bash/docker o /etc/bash_completiond/dockersh

     /etc/bash_completiond/dockersh
  • delete all images containing string

    docker operator">| function">grep operator"><search> function">awk string">'{print $1 ":" $2}' function">xargs rmi
